sentences.english: And i have no idea how the hell you get the impressions that Okinawans are pro-Chinese.
sentences.chinese: 我不知道你怎麼會有沖繩縣民親華的印象。

sentences.english: The deployment of troops on the areas west of Okinawa prefecture serves 2 purposes .
sentences.chinese: 在沖繩縣以西部署部隊有兩個目的。

sentences.english: Japan seized Ryukyu in 1879 and changed its name to Okinawa Prefecture.
sentences.chinese: 1879年，日本吞併琉球並改稱沖繩縣。

sentences.english: As a result, the Japanese government did not approve of the request of Okinawa Prefecture to set up sovereignty markers.
sentences.chinese: 因此，日本政府沒有同意沖繩縣建立國家標樁的請求。

sentences.english: Okinawa is the first place in all of Japan to see them bloom.
sentences.chinese: 沖繩縣是日本第一看見櫻花。

sentences.english: A rail less tram for tourist used by Cactus Park, Okinawa.
sentences.chinese: 行駛於沖繩縣仙人掌公園的環園賞花列車。
